arcade.patch.agent.cell

Class PatchCellCancer

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.patch.agent.cell.PatchCell
      • arcade.patch.agent.cell.PatchCellTissue
        • arcade.patch.agent.cell.PatchCellCancer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cell, java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PatchCellCancerStem

    public class PatchCellCancer
extends PatchCellTissue
    Extension of PatchCellTissue for cancerous tissue cells.

    PatchCellCancer agents are modified from their superclass:

    • If cell is quiescent, they may exit out of quiescence into undefined if there is space in their neighborhood
    See Also:
